				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I just wanted to say thank you, Oleg, for a superb piece of code. I started <span style="font-weight: bold">The Sudexel Discussion Board</span> a couple of weeks ago. Within 10 days, I was getting up to 6 spam-bot posts per day. Since I installed Textual Confirmation, 3 days ago, 27 Spam-bots have been blocked and none have got through.
<br />

<br />
Installation was &quot;A piece of cake&quot; for an amateur like me using <span style="font-weight: bold">EasyMod</span>. I would recommend this to anyone. It worked immediately with no problems. It's also great to see that this comes from Russia, which seems to be where most Spam-bots originate.
<br />

<br />
Many Thanks.
